    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/c610ed9c09b4b583fa84f1933227df40.poster.avif?t=1755123796\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/c610ed9c09b4b583fa84f1933227df40.webm?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/c610ed9c09b4b583fa84f1933227df40.mp4?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing Homaysa, a virtual reality experience for gamers and relaxation seekers alike. This collection of VR game modes and VR experiences offers players the chance to play, chat and relax in a multiplayer environment. With networked physics, Homaysa provides a suitable platform for gaming and simulations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the excitement of VR multiplayer gaming and immerse yourself in a collection of VR experiences and games with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/9cacca20338ab117f7cba983f1bc4d5f.poster.avif?t=1755123796\" width=800 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/9cacca20338ab117f7cba983f1bc4d5f.webm?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/9cacca20338ab117f7cba983f1bc4d5f.mp4?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Jump To Unreal Engine 5</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Homaysa has been rebuilt from scratch in Unreal Engine 5, that is why some of the old screenshots of the game are of the old build that was made in Unity, to reach the old build, simply go to the properties of Homaysa in Steam and click the &quot;Betas&quot; tap and on the right you would find an option for &quot;old_homaysa&quot;. The Unreal version has now replaced the current default version of Homaysa.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/70fb5e38bfbb46e8a01aa2acf88ecdf1.poster.avif?t=1755123796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/70fb5e38bfbb46e8a01aa2acf88ecdf1.webm?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/70fb5e38bfbb46e8a01aa2acf88ecdf1.mp4?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experiences and Game modes in the new Homaysa:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathmatch</strong>: Fight other players with assault rifles and sniper rifles in fast-paced, action-packed matches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moon</strong>: Explore the Moon, drive a car on it, check out its dark side, and see Earth from space in a spherical gravity planet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VR Lords</strong>: Control your own stone age soldiers to fight against an AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dungeon: </strong>Team up with friends to solve puzzles, fight monsters, and survive in this dark, creepy dungeon crawler. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swords Arena</strong>: Duel other players with swords in a medieval arena. Master your skills to become the champion. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mech Football/Soccer</strong>: Pilot a mech and play football (or soccer) with friends in a futuristic, high-energy sport.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax in Alien Planet</strong>: An area where players can relax in a night scene on another planet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Indoor Shooting Range</strong>: Experience VR shooting and see how good is your aim. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open Shooting Range</strong>: VR Shooting in an open area, with almost realistic graphics in VR.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax in Code</strong>: Chill in a VR space where code rains down around you, perfect for relaxing or brainstorming.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/f181c6a966798accb044a29bfaea0c47.poster.avif?t=1755123796\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/f181c6a966798accb044a29bfaea0c47.webm?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/f181c6a966798accb044a29bfaea0c47.mp4?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Things to experience in the Old Homaysa</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the &quot;old Homaysa&quot; version, players can engage in sword battles with others in the Sword Arena. Drive a space ship around planet Death. Or play Billiard with their friends in VR with a breath-taking view of Earth from space. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meanwhile, Chat &amp; Relax Land offers stunning environments such as a desert at night and space floating level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > How to play on Oculus Quest VR Headsets?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Start/Download the Meta Quest Link app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Pair your Oculus Quest headset to to the Meta Quest Link app by wire or wireless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Start Homaysa.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Homaysa community today and experience the next level of virtual reality gaming and relaxation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/191f7831bdafab8c4d68b017f65dab20.poster.avif?t=1755123796\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/191f7831bdafab8c4d68b017f65dab20.webm?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170860/extras/191f7831bdafab8c4d68b017f65dab20.mp4?t=1755123796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expect some bugs, active development is ongoing, we’re a 1 person team. Bear with us!</strong></h2>",
